  "body": "Normally after sending some tx eth.getBlockTransaction(\"pending\") will increase until the tx is mined. Currently the functions always return 1 even after a tx was sent locally. Affecting 0.9.32 and 0.9.35. Not sure where the bug is first introduced. Stats.ethdev.com confirms the observation. Judging by the number of tx mined per block (also=1) seems like the issue is real and not limited to reporting problem\n",
